%I A394230 #15 Mar 15 2026 19:42:15
%S A394230 1729,15,21,85,33,35,145,51,57,55,69,221,265,87,77,679,721,95,2101,
%T A394230 123,129,115,141,119,505,159,171,493,177,143,3421,255,161,685,213,219,
%U A394230 745,1603,237,187,249,203,865,267,209,235,1981,291,985,275,309,901,321,327,253,339,1145
%N A394230 a(n) is the least odd k such that A393131((k-1)/2) = EulerPhi(k)/A329726((k-1)/2) is 2*n; least odd k such that the witnesses for Solovay-Strassen primality test of k has index 2*n as a subgroup of (Z/kZ)*. a(n) = 0 if no such k exists.
%C A394230 Least odd k such that the index of {a in (Z/kZ)* : a^((k-1)/2) == Jacobi(a,k) (mod k)} has index 2*n in (Z/kZ)*.
%H A394230 Jianing Song, <a href="/A394230/b394230.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%H A394230 Louis Monier, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/0304-3975(80)90007-9">Evaluation and comparison of two efficient primality testing algorithms</a>, Theoretical Computer Science, Vol. 11 (1980), pp. 97-108.
%H A394230 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euler-Jacobi_pseudoprime">Euler-Jacobi pseudoprime</a>.
%H A394230 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solovay%E2%80%93Strassen_primality_test">Solovay-Strassen primality test</a>.
%e A394230 a(1) = 1729 since there are exactly phi(1729)/2 = 648 bases a in (Z/1729Z)* satisfying a^((1729-1)/2) == Jacobi(a,1729) (mod 1729), and 1729 is the smallest odd number with this property.
%e A394230 a(4) = 85 since there are exactly phi(85)/8 = 8 bases a in (Z/85Z)* satisfying a^((85-1)/2) == Jacobi(a,85) (mod 85), and 85 is the smallest odd number with this property. These bases are {1, 13, 16, 38, 47, 69, 72, 84}.
%o A394230 (PARI) SS(k) = my(f=factor(k), r=#f~); delta(k, f)*prod(i=1, r, gcd((k-1)/2, f[i, 1]-1)) \\ see A329726 for delta
%o A394230 index(k) = eulerphi(k)/SS(k)
%o A394230 first_n_terms(n) = my(v=vector(n), filled=0, i); forstep(k=3, oo, 2, if((i=index(k))<=2*n && i%2==0 && (i=i>>1) && v[i]==0, v[i]=k; filled++); if(filled==n, return(v)))
%Y A394230 Cf. A329726, A393131.
%K A394230 nonn,new
%O A394230 1,1
%A A394230 _Jianing Song_, Mar 13 2026
